name: Don't Dance 12" LP
description:
Newest release by The Monolators. This 12" vinyl record has a signed and numbered screen printed cover by Eli and Mary Monolator. Every run of 40 has a new color scheme. Current colors are Black and hot pink.

Tracks include:
1. I Must Be Dreaming
2. Oh No, Everything Has CHanged
3. Don't Dance
4. Hearts Going Steady
5. I Keep Knocking
6. CA-3A-569
7. I Heard Her Calling From ANother Room
8. Duchess
9. This Is Goodbye
10. Don't Dance (Reprise)

name: You Look Good On the Train 10" EP
description: This four song EP is not just the vinyl. It also packaged with a download card so that you can put it straight on your iPod. Songs include: the title track, You Look Good On the Train, Eagle Fighting Zebra, Weaker Self and At the Top Of the Stairs.©2007

name: Let's Be Best Friends In Space 7" Single
description: This single features the song, “Let’s Be Best Friends In Space” on the A side and “Kids On Fire” on the B side. The record is on grey swirl vinyl.©2005

name: Santa Claus Vs. Dave Matthews 7" Single
description: This is a special Christmas single stamped on RED vinyl with music that is not found on any album. Plus a very special message from the robot crime lord Mechanor.©2003
